items.name: Colored Lipstick - LoHa
items.description:
Please check out my Ko-Fi page if you are interested in supporting me.

LoRA commissions open! -> Fiverr

This is a LoHa LoRA! You need the extension! Why? They do a lot better with multi-concepts.
This LoHa is probably best used for INPAINTING. Not required tho! You can just prompt for it.

Trigger words for V4.20 (USE NEGATIVES FOR BETTER COLOR CONTROL) - green lips is VERY STRONG, use it with lower tag weight like "green lips:0.8":

positive: <lora:ColoredLipstickv420:0.7>(lipstick, green lips, blue dress)
and in negative: (green dress:1.5, green hair:1.5, green eyes:1.5)

You can try "white lips", "red lips", "pink lips", "orange lips", "purple lips", "green lips", "yellow lips", "gold lips", "brown lips", "blue lips" "black lips", "aqua lips" for colors (white and green aren't that good and orange only appears in high weight like 0.7-0.8).
Try to also describe the mouth or use tags that could influence the mouth, if possible, like "smile", "puckered lips", "lips apart", "open mouth" and "closed mouth".

Follow the steps in the Model Version notes to reproduce my images.

Sample images generated with AbyssOrangeMix3A1.

All negative embeds should be easy to find. and Prompts should be included in the sample images! Click the little icon in the bottom right to see it.


Could use same tags in negatives to control how it generates.

You might want to add some negatives, for example:
(makeup)

It was trained on 81 512x512 images scraped from the internet and 20 epochs using animefull_final.

Danbooru tags generated by Waifu Diffusion 1.4 Tagger and fine tuned for specific details like "blue lips" or "red lips".

The model loves to generate:

  • Everything but "white lips". :(

modelVersions.name: v4.20
modelVersions.description:
Generate using a weight of 0.4-1 like this: <lora:ColoredLipstickV420:0.8>.


How I archived my generations:

  1. txt2img: DPM++ SDE Karras with 20 steps, 512x512(can go up to 768 for wide or tall), Restore faces on (using CodeFormer weight 1.0 in Settings), Hires-fix on, to 1024x1024 (double original size) with your preferred upscaler and Denoise 0.4, CFG 7. Then send to img2img!

  2. img2img: DPM++ SED Karras with 20 steps, Restore faces on (CodeFormer weight 1), rescale to 1536x1536, CFG 7, Denoise between 0.3-0.7 (based on how much you want to improve the image), SAME PROMPT! Send to extras when happy with img2img/inpaint results.

  3. extras: Scale to x3 (final will be 4608x4608, I suggest going lower, I did x3 just for the samples here) Upscaler 1 - FatalAnime 4x, Upscaler 2 - SwinIR 4x with 0.10 visibility, GFPGAN 0.10 visibility, CodeFormer 0.10 visibility.

If anyone is curious about my version names: v{version}.{trainingEpochs}

items.name: Ruby O. Fee (Actress)
items.description:
A request of @tiziocf12.

Ruby O. Fee is a German-Costa Rican actress, known for her role in Army of Thieves, among other works.

This TI has been updated, Please check the "About this version" section for more info!

TI trained for 600 steps, with a gradual learning rate. I'll probably work on it again at some point, as I'm not convinced with certain tendencies of this embedding (for instance, her hair has a reddish hue that's probably a consequence of the dataset I chose, but it's easily fixable through prompting). But overall, I'm quite satisfied with what I see. Hope you like it!

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description: Kept training the previous embedding at a rate of 0.001 until step 1001. Seems improved overall, with some issues with they eyes apparently fixed. The tonality of her hair keeps being more reddish than I'd like, but it's so easy to fix that I think it's not worth retraining from scratch just for that, at least for now. Hope you like it!

items.name: BB95 Furry Mix
items.description:
V11.0 SE : This is a Special Edition of BB95. It's trained on a small, curated dataset of very high quality images, with the hope of improving the composition quality.

Most of the time, it will be better than v11. But in some cases, it will be worse than v11. It's not good enough to be a full, proper v12 with the kind of quality that's expected. It's a side-grade from v11.

In testing, it did better at higher resolutions, and the composition was better. Give it a try, see if you like it, and leave a review! If a lot of people say that it's an improvement, maybe the training can continue on a larger dataset.

Thanks to Dogarrowtype for the idea, and for helping me collect the dataset.

Please consider supporting me so I can continue to make more models --> https://www.patreon.com/BB95FurryMix

Don't forget to join the Furry Diffusion discord server --> https://discord.gg/furrydiffusion

Since v3, this model uses e621 tags.

This model is a mix of various furry models.

It's doing well on generating photorealistic male and female anthro, SFW and NSFW.

I HIGHLY recommend to use Hires Fix to have better results

Below is an example prompt for the v7/v6/v5/v4/v3/v2.

Positive:

anthro (white wolf), male, adult, muscular, veiny muscles, shorts, tail, (realistic fur, detailed fur texture:1.2), detailed background, outside background, photorealistic, hyperrealistic, ultradetailed,

Negative:

I recommend to use boring_e621, you can add bad-hands-v5 if you want

Settings :

Steps: 30-150

Sampler: DDIM or UniPC or Euler A

CFG scale: 7-14

Size: from 512x512 to 750x750 (only v4/v5/v6/v7)

Denoising strength: 0.6

Clip skip: 1

Hires upscale: 2

Hires steps: 30-150

Hires upscaler: Latent (nearest)

items.name: Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (AOC)

Modify the weights of the LoRA to achieve the desired result. The base model for SD 1.5 will look the best. However I had great results with Protogen, Dreamlike Photoreal, and Realistic Vision as well, and various blends.

This was also trained with the expanded VAE located here. Please use this VAE when inferring with this LoRA.

modelVersions.description:
Used bmaltais's implementation of kohya_ss LoRA training scripts.

Resumed training on the original 1.0 model with a bit more focus on full body photos. AOC at a distance will still require inpainting of the face. Training was resumed at 768x768 but the best generations will likely be 512x786 (portrait).

The sample images were generated with the base SD 1.5 model.

Total Images: 19 total high resolution images from the original dataset in version 1.0

Regularization Images: 300 total "sexy woman" regularization images from ProGamerGov's dataset at huggingface.

Training Steps: 2100 in 1.1, 4000 total including 1.0

items.name: Claymore Style
items.description:
Armored girls in the style of the Claymore manga by Norihiro Yagi

How to use
No trigger word, just use "1girl" and tags describing a claymore to prompt one. You can also just use "1girl" for a general style applicator.
See images for sample prompts for both.

Due to the dataset faces further away generally have to be inpainted.

Users of AOM2 might want to add "chibi,3d,realistic" to the negative tags to counteract its strict style changes. Or just use a model with better support for sketch and drawing type images.

Users of the AUTOMATIC1111 release can use the follow dynamic prompt as a general claymore generator

({upper|full} body)

(solo)

(1girl)(facing viewer)

({long|medium|short} white hair)

(({white|black} leotard)({white|black} armored skirt)({white|black} cape)(silver (pauldrons+gauntlets+greaves)))

Versions
This LoRA comes in two versions, one 8 and one 32 DIM sized. The former can be slightly more flexible and the latter slightly more detailed but the differences are fairly small.

Misc
512 resolution trained on NAI without noise offset option for best LoRA compatibility. Dataset based on 80 greyscale images from the Claymore Memorabilia Artbook.
Tested on NAI + AOM2.

All images except one or two are (slightly cherrypicked) txt2img gens for transparence, no inpainting done.

Don't forget to review and upload your own images, it's always fun to see what you're creating!
Like my LoRAs and want more? Please consider a small tip towards my electricity bill and further training >.<

items.name: Corset Piercing
items.description:
A model for corset piercings. I wasn't sure how it'd turn out considering the small data set but I am very impressed.

Quirks:
It will try to lift clothes so I would suggest 'clothes lift' in the negatives. There were only two images with lifted clothes, but with the size of the data set I guess that was a big deal.
On rare occasions it will put the zigzag-ing lace on the clothes like an actual corset ignoring the piercing.
Corset should go in the negatives to avoid getting them occasionally.
The piercing counts as clothes so when trying to prompt nudity with the piercing do '(nude:0.8)' in order to not remove it.

Things to try:
Try placing the piercing where you want it. It will do 'corset piercing on': back, thigh, stomach, or arm.
Try changing the color. It does red or black very easily but it can also handle similar colors such as pink or dark blue.
Try it on realistic models. From some testing it works well!
Try it without prompting for the piercing as it makes cool outfits.
Try it with my goth LoRA. The last image was made with both.

As usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demos are Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 0.8
Note the last image is using my Goth LoRA as well in case that was missed earlier
NSFW images towards the end of the demos

If you get any cool gens share them in the comments!

modelVersions.name: v3.15
modelVersions.description:
Generate using a weight of 0.5-1 like this: <lora:CumOnTongev315:0.7>.


How I archived my generations:

  1. txt2img: DPM++ SDE Karras with 20 steps, 512x512(can go up to 768 for wide or tall), Restore faces on (using CodeFormer weight 1.0 in Settings), Hires-fix on, to 1024x1024 (double original size) with your preferred upscaler and Denoise 0.5, CFG 7. Then send to img2img!

  2. img2img: DPM++ SED Karras with 20 steps, Restore faces on (CodeFormer weight 1), rescale to 1536x1536, CFG 7, Denoise between 0.3-0.7 (based on how much you want to improve the image), SAME PROMPT! Send to extras when happy with img2img/inpaint results.

  3. extras: Scale to x3 (final will be 4608x4608, I suggest going lower, I did x3 just for the samples here) Upscaler 1 - FatalAnime 4x, Upscaler 2 - SwinIR 4x with 0.10 visibility, GFPGAN 0.10 visibility, CodeFormer 0.10 visibility.

If anyone is curious about my version names: v{version}.{trainingEpochs}

items.name: Guizhong (Genshin Impact) LoRA
items.description:
This is a LoRA of Guizhong from Genshin Impact.

Compatibility

Trained on the NovelAI model, and is therefore compatible with any anime-styled model such as Counterfeit, AOM, and PastelMix. The example images are generated from the above three models.

Features

  • Dress up Guizhong in alternate outfits. This is done by replacing the default_outfit tag with the tags of whatever cloths you want her to wear. This may require some fiddling. Examples are given in the sample images

  • This LoRA not only does well on rendering Guizhong's front, but also her back. Again, examples are given in the samples

  • Use the tag sleeves over wrists to give almost any outfit you prompt on Guizhong have her floppy sleeves

  • Can do lewds if prompted

Bugs

  • Sometimes the lora will try to give Guizhong stockings of sorts, you can prompt this out with barefoot, but it will end up with the image focus more on her feet

  • Due to the character's floppy sleeves and her nonexistent dataset(fan art), sometimes the lora can't discern where her arms are and ends up making a mess. Just reroll the generator gacha

  • Using starry sky print is supposed to give her outfit a more pronounced starry night sky color motif, but it bleeds over to the actual sky as well

Recommended Weight

Generating at weight = 1.0 produces good results for all occasions. When attempting to prompt for different outfits or poses, lowering the weight to 0.8 may give better results(untested).

items.name: GAZ2410
items.description:
https://t.me/stdif_kos

ГАЗ-24-10 «Волга» — советский и российский автомобиль среднего класса производства Горьковского автомобильного завода. Выпускался с конца 1985 года до 1993 года. Представляет собой модификацию модели ГАЗ-24 с изменённым внешним видом ("рестайлинг"): травмобезопасными наружными ручками открывания дверей от ГАЗ-3102, интерьером от него же, отсутствием форточек в передних дверях и заднего стояночного огня, а также были убраны хромовая полоса с крышки багажника и шильдики "Волга" с передних крыльев[источник не указан 238 дней]. Через год после начала выпуска также стала отличаться пластмассовой чёрной облицовкой — решёткой радиатора[1]. Является паллиативом, обусловленным наложением вето на крупносерийный выпуск модели ГАЗ-3102. При этом машина сохранила относительно высокое качество сборки и репутацию надёжного автомобиля, несмотря на морально устаревшую конструкцию. Помимо базового седана, ГАЗ-24-10 выпускался в трёх вариантах для службы такси (бензиновый седан ГАЗ-24-11, газомоторный седан ГАЗ-24-17 и бензиновый универсал ГАЗ-24-14), универсал также предлагался в базовом виде (ГАЗ-24-12) и как карета скорой помощи (ГАЗ-24-13)[2]. Помимо этого, существовало множество мелкосерийных моделей, в том числе «догонялка» с двигателем V8, (ГАЗ-24-34). В 1991 году её сменила модель ГАЗ-31029, также представлявшая собой паллиативную модернизацию ГАЗ-24-10 на базе ГАЗ-3102. Всего был собран 417 481 экземпляр различных модификаций данного автомобиля[3].

items.name: Tsukino
items.description:
First off, yes, it can do her normal proportions. I'm just being safe with the image choices.
Second, the LoRA is marked as NSFW because it is hard to put clothes on her.

IMPORTANT TAGS (remove what you don't want):
anthro, blue eyes, leotard, brown body, brown fur, female, female anthro, fur, hair, neckerchief, paws, pink hair, stripes, tail, thick thighs, felid, felyne, lynian, mammal, tsukino \(monster hunter stories\), capcom, monster hunter, monster hunter stories, monster hunter stories 2 wings of ruin, skulkers

For Human Ver:
blue eyes, leotard, brown body, hair, neckerchief, pink hair, stripes, tail, thick thighs, tsukino \(monster hunter stories\), capcom, monster hunter, monster hunter stories, monster hunter stories 2 wings of ruin, skulkers

NOTES:
It really likes thick thighs so if you use the LoRA but prompt something other than the character with the 'thick thighs' tag and a lower LoRA weight you can get some good results.

As Always:
Trained on Anything v3
Demo is Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 0.8

items.name: Satellite Image Generator - MapSatimageEU - Cloudless LoRa
items.description:
This model has been trained a dataset based on the publicly available cloudless satellite imagery of the European region by https://s2maps.eu/. The emphasis of the training And not a state editing, is to allow for realistic satellite imagery look while prepossessing the satellite source images to remove noise and artefacts that compromise the display features. specially stitching errors and offset lines from the original satellite pictures have been removed prior to starting the Training.

link to cp https://civitai.com/models/17866/satellite-image-generator-mapsatimageeu-cloudless-cp

If you're interested in the edited training data, feel free to get in contact. I refrained from uploading it since its over 12 GB of imagery.
